<plot>Two recently fired pizzeria employees who each independently decide to take revenge against their former employer. Their plan? Burglarizing his home on Christmas Eve. The surprise of running into another burglar leads to a disastrous fight that leaves them both tied up in Christmas Tree lights. As a result, they are forced to work together to escape and complete their vengeful mission. Hilarity ensues.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?104970</url></doc>
